node.text:
Did you start sweating while watching this? 🤯 This spine-tingling footage shows aerobatic pilot, Timur Fatkullin @aero.tim, skydiving above the Carpathian Mountains. 🔥

Also known as the Carpathians, the mountain range forms an arc throughout Central and Eastern Europe. It's a treasure trove of biodiversity, with many brown bears, wolves, lynxes, bison, and rare birds calling it home. 🌳

📽 @aero.tim 
📍 Carpathian Mountains, Europe
🎶 Lovely - Billie Eilish & Khalid
♻️ Post via @beautifuldestinations
